metadata.name: Getting lost in Venice
metadata.description:
Hidden corners in the Venetian maze (Venice, Italy).

**Taken**: July 2020
**Camera**: Sony A7III + Sony 70-200mm G
**Post**: Manual multi long exposure, fusion of 12 shots
